4. Combine Fetch and Post (CRUD Integration)
Objective: Build a two-way integration with an external system.

Challenge:

Integrate Salesforce with Google Sheets API.
Fetch data from a Google Sheet and create/update Salesforce records (e.g., Contacts).
When a new Contact is created in Salesforce, push the details back to the Google Sheet.
Bonus:

Handle edge cases like duplicate records or API rate limits.
Build a button in LWC to manually sync data on demand.
